<dl id="n12113h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12113h">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12113h"> 113(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> burning <font face="wake">+</font>ians (barbars)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> c&apos;&eacute;tait alors la jeunesse de la civilisation chr&eacute;tienne et ces barbares, en qui bouillonnaient des passions si violentes, avaient au c&oelig;ur des tr&eacute;sors d&apos;h&eacute;roisme <br><font color="green">[&hellip; this was the infancy of Christian civilisation, and the barbarians, in whom violent passions burned, had in their heart treasures of heroism]</font> <small> <a name="STCM" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#STCM"><cite title="source">Saint Colomban</cite></a> (1905) 44</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
